text.section:
The Web site shall be in a searchable format and shall provide financial information about expenditures not exempt under the provisions of state or federal law, including:
The payee name;
The category or type of expenditure;
A description of the reason for the expenditure, if available;
The expenditure amount;
An electronic link to documents relating to the expenditure, if the documents are available electronically;
The budget adopted by the district and subsequent amendments to that budget;
The completed annual audit; and
Any other information deemed relevant by the district.
